<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٧٩٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5178">قَبِيصَةُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2521">أَبِي حَازِمٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2676">سَهْلِ بْنِ سَعْدٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>: عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«الرَّوْحَةُ وَالْغَدْوَةُ فِي سَبِيلِ اللهِ أَفْضَلُ مِنَ الدُّنْيَا وَمَا فِيهَا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>